{"tid":1953750,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張國榮逝世 17 周年 中環文華獻花","createTime":"2020-04-01T10:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T11:09:57.000Z","uid":183383,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc12b6f03596d528e59c4e461878af15a451db5","tid":1953750,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:51:24.000Z","msg":"今日是張國榮逝世 17 周年，中環文華酒店外有人擺放花束悼念，其中一束寫上「願『榮』光歸香港」。<br />\n<br />\n由於疫情關係，香港張國榮歌迷會早前宣布首度停辦粉絲獻花及群聚悼念活動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zdxUbEK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzdxUbEK.jpg&h=bde3a71c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n哩個女仔係唔係小美黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文章重溫：<br />\n<br />\n疫症時期悼念張國榮 ／ 洛楓<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UTn45Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UTn45Y&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=a3905edf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UTn45Y</a><br />\n<br />\n他的孤獨，成就經典／李展鵬<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WXn8V6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WXn8V6&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=5492ed9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WXn8V6</a><br />\n<br />\n張國榮：原來眞正的天堂是香港 今日回想格外唏噓／黃宇軒<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3dKiK1D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3dKiK1D&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=05dd8c5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3dKiK1D</a><br />\n<br />\n是無力或有心像謎像戲的《有心人》︰張國榮 ／ 愛美麗<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3azaob9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3azaob9&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=a8cf85d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3azaob9</a><br />\n<br />\n《家有囍事》「家明表哥」眼中的 Leslie／袁文傑<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/39raIaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39raIaw&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=009344c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/39raIaw</a><br />\n<br />\n1997 年的一雙高跟鞋：張國榮與香港身份／李展鵬<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2noCTin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2noCTin&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=a628099e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2noCTin</a><br />\n<br />\n春天該很好，你若尚在場／過路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2THGZlL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2THGZlL&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=62885526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2THGZlL</a><br />\n<br />\n哥哥,我地好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ae13416e12b0586657351fb4e593db0bc9fdec","tid":1953750,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:54:41.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"6c5f5808aa70b5cd67f75d1983e481c6fcaad691","tid":1953750,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77cd1cc6b6a7b9147790d10cbd1ec787498f46c4","tid":1953750,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:55:24.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"330307e1b27f35ba3ee5063692b8a0fde6080e9a","tid":1953750,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413689e8abbbf57b26f17f447c00a3964bc7be45","tid":